      <section class="biography" id="biography">
        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Jonathan Marron is the Director General of Community and Social Care at the Department of Health and Social Care.  Prior to this role Jonathan has had a range of roles across the health service including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Director for Primary, Community, Mental Health and 7 Day Services at Department of Health and Social Care</li>
  <li>Director of Strategy at Public Health England</li>
  <li>Transition Director at Public Health England</li>
  <li>Director of Strategy and Planning at NHS South West Essex PCT</li>
  <li>Policy Director at Monitor</li>
  <li>System Reform and Commissioning Lead at Department of Health and Social Care</li>
</ul>

<p>Jonathan lives in London with his partner and 2 children.</p>
</div>
      </section>

      <div class="current-roles" id="current-roles">
          <section class="role_appointment role" id="role_appointment_4678">
            <h1 id="director-general-community-and-social-care">Director General, Community and Social Care</h1>
            <div class="govspeak">
<p>The Director General for Community and Social Care is responsible for the following policy areas:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Care and Transformation</li>
  <li>Metal Health, Dementia and Disabilities</li>
  <li>Medicines and Pharmacy</li>
  <li>Digital, Data and Primary Care</li>
  <li>the Office of the Chief Social Worker</li>
</ul>

</div>
            <div class="read-more">
                <p class="js-hide-other-departments organisations-name-list">
  <a class="organisation-link" href="/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care">Department of Health and Social Care</a>
</p>

            </div>
